WEBVTT

00:00.290 --> 00:02.095
Previously on "Six"...

00:02.098 --> 00:03.887
Wait, wait! I'm American!

00:03.890 --> 00:05.293
I'm from Detroit, okay?

00:05.296 --> 00:07.093
Don't...

00:07.094 --> 00:08.659
What the...

00:08.660 --> 00:10.223
He was a threat.

00:10.224 --> 00:12.465
- Erase that. - He was an
unarmed American who surrendered.

00:12.467 --> 00:15.013
Just deal with it, Caulder. This is war.

00:15.014 --> 00:17.553
And we are warriors, not savages!

00:17.554 --> 00:19.013
I won't do another op with you ever.

00:19.014 --> 00:20.463
How come you and Rip never had kids?

00:20.464 --> 00:22.843
Are you kidding me? He's
got teenage boys already.

00:22.844 --> 00:24.673
Boko Haram captured Richard Taggart,

00:24.674 --> 00:26.446
former troop chief of this command.

00:27.384 --> 00:28.723
He's there because of you.

00:28.724 --> 00:31.133
What are you doing, Michael?

00:31.134 --> 00:32.923
What needs to be done.

00:32.924 --> 00:34.673
Your new owners have arrived.

00:34.674 --> 00:36.173
I got a dead Boko Haram.

00:36.174 --> 00:37.554
What the hell?

00:40.924 --> 00:44.051
These are soldiers.
Trained, geared up, armored.

00:46.554 --> 00:49.054
Akmal, show us what Esther
and Na'omi are wearing.

00:51.464 --> 00:53.673
Make me believe it.

00:53.674 --> 00:55.883
My name is Richard Taggart.

00:55.884 --> 00:59.303
I was nothing more
than a hired assassin.

00:59.306 --> 01:00.966
Committed war crimes.

01:03.764 --> 01:06.053
The President of the United States

01:06.054 --> 01:08.463
wants to go on TV and tell the world

01:08.464 --> 01:10.515
that Richard Taggart is an American hero

01:10.518 --> 01:13.173
and that this confession
is pure bullshit.

01:13.174 --> 01:14.557
It is, right?

01:14.560 --> 01:16.053
Sir, there's no way
that Rip would say that.

01:16.054 --> 01:18.053
Not unless he was coerced... Or worse.

01:18.054 --> 01:20.843
We checked the ISR footage, and
there's a gap in the coverage

01:20.844 --> 01:22.615
when this was supposed to have happened.

01:22.617 --> 01:25.301
- <font color="#D81D1D">Synced and corrected by VitoSilans</font> -

01:25.304 --> 01:28.203
The other Muj was turned over
to the Afghan police... SOP.

01:28.206 --> 01:30.434
-- <font color="#138CE9">www.Addic7ed.com</font> --

01:30.437 --> 01:33.647
Anything you want to
add, now is the time.

01:40.804 --> 01:42.383
Sir, we need to get Rip

01:42.384 --> 01:45.223
before they torture him any more.

01:45.224 --> 01:47.786
Did we get any news on that
Chechen we bagged in Nigeria?

01:47.789 --> 01:49.463
Yeah, we're working
on a link between him

01:49.464 --> 01:53.673
and an ex-Spetsnaz guy
named Akmal Barayev.

01:53.674 --> 01:56.554
We thought he was dead, but
turns out he might not be.

01:59.969 --> 02:02.639
Chase, Fishbait, can you
guys give us a minute?

02:07.384 --> 02:08.964
You trust me with your life, Ortiz?

02:11.634 --> 02:13.173
Yes, Chase, I do.

02:13.174 --> 02:14.383
Then trust me.

02:14.384 --> 02:16.593
You know, he's right.

02:16.594 --> 02:18.263
We're either on this team or we're not.

02:18.264 --> 02:19.723
Okay.

02:19.724 --> 02:21.223
So, what's on your mind?

02:21.224 --> 02:23.264
Everything Rip says is true, right?

02:26.976 --> 02:28.106
Of course it's true.

02:34.245 --> 02:36.513
Caulder, what'd you do with
the photo of that dead guy?

02:36.514 --> 02:38.723
The one that I took for
the shooter statement.

02:38.724 --> 02:40.384
I erased it.

02:42.046 --> 02:43.550
Who else knows about this?

02:45.554 --> 02:47.343
Just the other Muj.

02:47.344 --> 02:48.843
The one with him... The driver.

02:48.844 --> 02:50.463
This is on us.

02:50.464 --> 02:52.513
Okay? You could lose
your trident... or worse.

02:52.514 --> 02:55.133
Look, what Rip did, shooting that kid,

02:55.134 --> 02:57.053
it's not what I signed up for.

02:57.054 --> 02:59.803
The bottom line...
We're on the right side.

02:59.806 --> 03:01.524
You know what... I signed up

03:01.527 --> 03:05.336
to help people who
can't help themselves.

03:05.339 --> 03:07.173
Like those girls who got kidnapped.

03:07.176 --> 03:08.136
We all did.

03:10.724 --> 03:11.803
Okay?

03:11.804 --> 03:13.803
Stay out of this.

03:13.804 --> 03:15.763
You got a bright future.
Don't screw it up.

03:15.764 --> 03:18.379
Walk out, brother.

03:19.929 --> 03:21.429
You were never here.

03:29.464 --> 03:30.843
Ortiz residence.

03:30.844 --> 03:33.633
Who's calling?

03:33.634 --> 03:35.133
You're from New York?

03:35.134 --> 03:37.263
Oh, The New Yorker. Magazine?

03:37.264 --> 03:38.513
Give it to me.

03:38.514 --> 03:40.923
Come on, give it to me.

03:40.924 --> 03:43.264
Yes? Who are you asking about?

03:45.134 --> 03:46.633
Never heard of him.

03:46.634 --> 03:49.223
You must have the wrong number, buddy.

03:49.224 --> 03:50.692
He asked about Rip.

03:50.695 --> 03:52.479
Yeah. Come on, let's,
um... Let's have dinner.

03:52.481 --> 03:54.013
I'm not hungry.

03:54.014 --> 03:55.963
Why? You're not feeling well?

03:55.964 --> 03:58.263
Everyone was talking
about Rip today at school.

03:58.264 --> 04:00.174
I watched that video.

04:04.764 --> 04:06.723
Okay, guys.

04:06.724 --> 04:08.053
Listen to me, okay?

04:08.054 --> 04:11.013
Um... it's gonna be fine,

04:11.014 --> 04:15.763
but it's, uh... It's a tough situation.

04:15.764 --> 04:19.882
Someone is forcing Uncle Rip
to say a lot of bad things.

04:19.884 --> 04:22.464
But we're gonna bring
him back safe and sound.

04:28.123 --> 04:31.243
He was an American?
The guy that Rip killed?

04:35.764 --> 04:39.174
He might come over here and
kill Anabel and Ricky Jr.?

04:40.563 --> 04:43.477
Ricky, I made peace a long
time ago with what you do.

04:46.224 --> 04:50.723
I don't care if Rip killed him.

04:50.724 --> 04:54.513
I care about you, about us.

04:54.514 --> 04:56.674
That's what I care about.

05:02.264 --> 05:04.634
To my brothers on SEAL Team Six...

05:07.264 --> 05:10.223
...look inside your hearts.

05:10.224 --> 05:12.883
Let your better nature...

05:12.884 --> 05:16.884
let the truth... Let it shine through.

05:18.844 --> 05:22.423
It's not too late. I am proof of that.

05:22.424 --> 05:24.383
Congrats, Rip.

05:24.384 --> 05:26.263
You're a real hero now.

05:26.264 --> 05:28.351
It's already the most
popular video in the world.

05:28.354 --> 05:29.466
Recruiting's through the roof.

05:29.468 --> 05:30.856
The SEALs, your families, they're all...

05:30.858 --> 05:31.977
They won't believe it.

05:31.980 --> 05:32.963
I only said those things

05:32.964 --> 05:36.093
'cause you put a
suicide vest on a woman.

05:36.094 --> 05:38.554
And a 13-year-old child.

05:40.224 --> 05:41.384
You're right.

05:44.054 --> 05:46.093
I apologize for that.

05:46.094 --> 05:48.673
I know you love these girls.

05:48.674 --> 05:50.593
My little brother's name was Omar.

05:50.594 --> 05:52.633
It means "long lived."

05:52.634 --> 05:55.763
He was born premature.

05:55.764 --> 05:57.963
My first memory is going to the hospital

05:57.964 --> 06:00.883
and watching my mother
cry outside the ICU.

06:00.884 --> 06:03.593
She could only hold him
for 20 minutes a day.

06:03.594 --> 06:08.723
It almost bankrupted my
father, but Omar made it.

06:08.724 --> 06:10.513
He was the smallest kid on the block,

06:10.514 --> 06:12.463
but he never backed down.

06:12.464 --> 06:14.093
He hated injustice.

06:14.094 --> 06:16.924
He hated the strong preying on the weak.

06:20.224 --> 06:21.883
And then you murdered him.

06:21.886 --> 06:24.214
If you're looking for blood,
look on your own hands.

06:25.964 --> 06:29.553
Now, you're a good woman. A teacher.

06:29.554 --> 06:31.799
But you have no idea

06:31.802 --> 06:34.500
what kind of a man
Richard Taggart really is.

